              "id": "CVE-2026-40228",
              "name": "OsPackageVulnerability",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "systemd: systemd-journald: Unintended output to user terminals via logger command"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "In systemd 259, systemd-journald can send ANSI escape sequences to the terminals of arbitrary users when a \"logger -p emerg\" command is executed, if ForwardToWall=yes is set."
